{"tid":2496213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：香港最壞時候已過，料今年經濟增長3至5%","createTime":"2021-04-19T16:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T07:35:59.000Z","uid":278587,"like":4,"dislike":216,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6d322bd23ef3b2608aababee4529998a3f661e","tid":2496213,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=431700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431700&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=734e3d76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431700&h=aa1d076d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=431700</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥在海南出席博鰲亞洲論壇，她接受中央電視台訪問，稱香港先後經歷反修例示威及全球疫情打擊，但最壞的時間已過，相信今年經濟增長有3%至5%。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥：「一個是中美貿易糾紛，到2019年中往後一年，我們受到社會動盪，黑暴的影響的厲害，那麼當然就過去十多個月，是全球新冠的疫情。在多重的打擊下，難免我們會出現的經濟的逆轉，所以現在看來，我們最壞的時間已經過了，我們估計今年2021年，應該是有年度的增長，大概是3%至5%。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，西方政客針對香港的批評，是他們看到中國富強起來，心裡不舒服，目的想要圍堵中國，所以難以改變他們的看法，她會集中精力處理香港的事務。"},{"pid":"d1d1b63e5ec3b407bbb8070e884d2093f7e6b183","tid":2496213,"uid":361975,"like":129,"dislike":1,"score":128,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:07:05.000Z","msg":"有你條仆街係到點會過呀"},{"pid":"55590fc9888825419077a1e6b79c991e21eb2518","tid":2496213,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7421e6e6218ed3c5b3d8540aa16453bbaf7c333c","tid":2496213,"uid":38528,"like":90,"dislike":3,"score":87,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"有你條撚樣係到,-3-5%就有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cl